{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"DHTML","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/DHTML","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>DHTML</strong> 是動態 (<em>dynamic</em>) HTML 的縮短形式，且通常用於指那些未使用 flash 或 java 等外掛的交互式網頁後面的程式碼。The term aggregates the combined functionality 允許網頁開法者使用 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML\">HTML</a>， <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS\">CSS</a>，<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document_Object_Model\">Document Object Model</a>，以及 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript\">JavaScript</a>。</p>\n<p>DHTML 與 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/AJAX\">Ajax</a> 的不同之處在於，在載入階段它仍然基於 HTML, CSS 和 JS 等程式碼來定義。相反的，基於 Ajax 的頁面則使用 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\"><code>XMLHttpRequest</code></a> 介面來動態載入更多的資料。</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"DHTML 是動態 (dynamic) HTML 的縮短形式，且通常用於指那些未使用 flash 或 java 等外掛的交互式網頁後面的程式碼。The term aggregates the combined functionality 允許網頁開法者使用 HTML， CSS，Document Object Model，以及 JavaScript。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"DHTML","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"DHTML","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"DHTML","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"DHTML","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"DHTML","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"DHTML","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/glossary/dhtml","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/glossary/dhtml/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary","title":"術語表"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/DHTML","title":"DHTML"}],"pageTitle":"DHTML - 術語表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}